        <!-- Game start dialog -->
        <li Class="ScenPart_GameStartDialog">
          <def>GameStartDialog</def>
          <text>Here you arrive with your fireteam to complete a fool's errand. Before you can create a fortified FOB, a makeshift shelter will have to do.
		  
Words of Big Boss echo in your mind "Listen up. For us, there is no victory." 
one of the soldiers timidly objected, "But in revolution, doesn't one triumph or die?"

Big Boss coldly answered with "We don't do either." as he turned and walked away.</text>
          <closeSound>RH_MSFOpeningSting</closeSound>
